name: Bike and Walk Commutes
content:
Description: Data on bicycling and walking to work in the United States: 2008-2012.

[Source](https://github.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/tree/master/data/2019/2019-11-05) and second [source](https://www.census.gov/library/publications/2014/acs/acs-25.html?#)

Columns:

 * city (string): City name
 * state Enrollment (string): State name
 * city_size (string): City Size (Small = 20K to 99,999, Medium = 100K to 199,999, Large = >= 200K)
 * mode (string): Mode of transport, either walk or bike
 * n (numerical): Number of individuals
 * percent (numerical): Percent of total individuals
 * moe (numerical): Margin of Error (percent)
 * state_abb (string): Abbreviated state name
 * state_region (string): ACS State Region
